Build-Depends-Indep: debhelper (>> 3.0.0)
Standards-Version: 3.5.8

Package: caspar
Architecture: all
Depends: make
Suggests: jade, jadetex, tetex-bin, w3m, gs-common, psutils, lpr, postscript-viewer, man-db, docbook-dsssl
Description: Makefile snippets for common tasks
 Caspar offers Makefile snippets for common tasks, like installing system
 configuration files you maintain using CVS, or typesetting LaTeX, DocBook
 XML and DocBook SGML documents.  You'll need at least jade, jadetex and
 tetex-bin from the suggested packages if you want to do any typesetting.
